main event: A report of a pulsating, reddish-orange spherical object hovering and maneuvering rapidly in various directions, about 100-200 feet above the ground.
interesting points: The object appeared to be about 30-40 feet in diameter and gave off a brilliant, pulsating light.
The object sometimes disappeared and then reappeared.
The witness observed the object for approximately 15 minutes before it disappeared from view.
The witness had no explanation for what they saw.
The report states that the object seemed to send out beams of light in various directions.
